          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen food has great taste and made with proper hygiene and is affordable no overpricing.",
          "name": "Tejas Parate Parate",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen and parking lot is very good and big",
